Method to install :
Step 1: Install Dependencies (if needed)
If you're running this locally, ensure you have Node.js installed. Then, inside your project folder, install dependencies: "npm install"
Step 2: Run Locally (Test Before Deployment)
Start the app in development mode: 
"npm run dev"  # If using Vite
# OR
"npm start"    # If using Create React App
Step 3: Deploy Your Game Online
There are multiple ways to deploy your game:
Option 1: Deploy on Vercel (Fast & Free)
Install Vercel CLI if you haven't: "npm install -g vercel"
Login to Vercel:vercel login
Deploy: "vercel"
Vercel will provide a live URL for your game.
